{"tid":972684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU買樓買地勁賺1610萬？疑投機遭網民批評","createTime":"2019-01-07T14:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T19:50:34.000Z","uid":29627,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb72abf13fd2017bfdf4f05f9973c19535f4859","tid":972684,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"IU買樓買地勁賺1610萬？疑投機遭網民批評 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190107/large/1546832518_6be3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190107%2Flarge%2F1546832518_6be3.jpg&h=03871bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190107/large/1546832523_921d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190107%2Flarge%2F1546832523_921d.jpg&h=c29e198f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU方面否認投機<br />\n<br />\n韓國「國民妹妹」IU今日爆出是非，有韓媒表示IU於去年1月喺京畿道果川市果川洞以45億韓圜（約3,150萬港元）嘅價格，購買建築物及土地，因政府推廣GTX（Great Train Express）而令IU嘅物業升值23億韓圜（約1,610萬港元）。有韓國網民就質疑IU當初購入建築物及土地就係以賺取差價為目的嘅投機行為。<br />\n<br />\n隨後IU所屬事務所回應：「指IU投機嘅講法並唔係事實，佢完全冇投機目的，IU係以實際使用為目的而購買該建築物。目前該建築物內有IU母親嘅辦公室、IU嘅個人工作室、IU支持後輩而設立嘅練習室，佢並冇出售該建築物嘅打算。同時，報道中揭露嘅市價差價係唔可能出現嘅，23億韓圜呢個數字，本身就唔係正確嘅資訊。」又指IU購買嘅建築物及土地都唔喺GTX開發範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190107/59113278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F59113278&d=za12ywSivCnp80l6%2BeUfgwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f8279182\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F59113278&h=78956a1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190107/59113278</a>"},{"pid":"d20b8e7c0700dcc9fe990b06155f5d32007c0510","tid":972684,"uid":167566,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:24:52.000Z","msg":"......<br />\n韓國D網民係唔係痴撚線"},{"pid":"4dcc490c782a17cad9b07bffe927d32cd7e599be","tid":972684,"uid":555,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"就算係又有咩問題"},{"pid":"00bbca0b4b9f8f68459e7fb61b63abe6a0abf2db","tid":972684,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"投機你都識講，中就屌咁買完跌IU又有無好似好似香港人咁出黎屌人咩？"},{"pid":"7b6d49820519fe5e72e7131dc5bbe81697b9f859","tid":972684,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:35:58.000Z","msg":"慘到"},{"pid":"5ae1cced40b976c89a6acc5a25f2d842df9a1efc","tid":972684,"uid":75610,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d20b8e7c0700dcc9fe990b06155f5d32007c0510","tid":972684,"uid":167566,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:24:52.000Z","msg":"......<br />\n韓國D網民係唔係痴撚線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"揾錢都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e566c442ca916112f2e32c5aacd1681fb6637eb5","tid":972684,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"投機都有問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常買賣<br />\n死窮撚酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e3bad5c40b3c03bfbb55a0d44134ae5a8091f1","tid":972684,"uid":25924,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"明買明賣都比人屌<br />\n酸撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no